content: wtfsayo: Merged 8 PRs this week, with significant UI enhancements in #4393 (-5367 lines) and substantial work on authentication in #4420 (+707/-346 lines). Notable contributions include adding model/plugin name logging (#4394), extending OpenAI plugin support for custom embedding endpoints (#4421), and implementing unique PGLite folder functionality (#4423), while also providing 3 code reviews and adding 11 PR comments across the project.
